Hi Terry

The replacement drum uses a Mazda 3900 33 065 seal,  BTDT

I put them in stock at Airhead Parts a few years back.  Getting the
drums has been a nightmare though.

http://www.airheadparts.com/vintage-vw-parts/new-last-12-months/seal-front-wheel-l-or-r-211405641c

